The <code><strong>MouseEvent</strong></code> interface represents events that occur due to the user interacting with a pointing device (such as a mouse). Common events using this interface include <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/click" title="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/click">click</a></code>, <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/dblclick" title="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/dblclick">dblclick</a></code>, <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/mouseup" title="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/mouseup">mouseup</a></code>, <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/mousedown" title="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/mousedown">mousedown</a></code>.